<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Chasey</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>1999-12-09 17:18:17</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>After looking at the prices posted for the smasher i'll have to say I got really really lucky to buy mine for 162pp! :) Maybe it is because I am on the nameless server and and our economy is very cash poor?<BR>
<BR>
Anyways, i started a Dwarf warrior and gave her my backup Smasher and a shield to start with. After 48 hrs of game play she is level 21 and still using the smasher with a PGT or Langseax 1h in the offhand. The incredible thing is that with Double attack and Dual wield she routinely gets quad hits and critical hits up to 30. A fight usually goes something like this:<BR>
<BR>
A deepwater Caiman bites you for 20 damage<BR>
You crush a Deepwater Caiman for 12 points<BR>
You crush a Deepwater Caiman for 13 points<BR>
You slash a Deepwater Caiman for 13 points<BR>
You crush a Deepwater Caiman for 10 points<BR>
You crush a Deepwater Caiman for 9 points<BR>
You Kick a Deepwater Caiman for 8 points<BR>
A deepwater Caiman bites you for 18 damage<BR>
<BR>
Well, not everytime  but you get the picture :)<BR>
<BR>
